Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on predicting post popularity on Instagram, which involves analyzing images and captions. Computer vision techniques are used to extract features from images and incorporate them into the model. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper deals with social media data mining and predicting post popularity on Instagram, which falls under the scope of social and information networks. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with analyzing both images and captions, which are forms of multimedia. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with analyzing captions, which involves natural language processing techniques. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with predicting post popularity, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
